  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lankan support to Dallas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lanka Freedom Party has decided to support Mr. Dallas Alahapperuma in the election of a President.",
        "Mr. Aravinda Kumar mentions that he also informed the Central Committee of the party he represents about his decision.",
        "Accordingly, the Secretary General said that nine people representing the party will vote for Mr. Dallas Alahapperuma."
      ],
